*quodlibet-0.20.1-r1 (11 May 2006)

  11 May 2006; Thomas Cort <tcort@gentoo.org> +quodlibet-0.20.1-r1.ebuild:
  Added gst-plugins-gconf to DEPEND wrt Bug #133043 (Thanks to Frittella
  Laurento <mrfree@infinito.it>), removed the epatch lines which set the
  default pipeline (gst-plugins-gconf does this automatically), wrote a better
  DESCRIPTION, and changed pyvorbis depend to >=pyvorbis-1.4-r1 since the
  double free issue with 1.4 is solved in 1.4-r1.

